  *This is my first attempt at writing tab, so I hope it isn't too hard to read.*  
  *The brackets show parts that I will refer to down below.*  
  *-Intro-*  
  [G----------------------------------|  
  D-----2--2-2-0-2-2-5-5--[4]--4-4---|  
  A----------------------------------|  
  E----------------------------------|]  
  *-Chorus-       ^ = play 8 times (more or less)*  
  [G----------------------------------|  
  D-----2^----0^-[2-2-------0-0]-----|  
  A--------3^----[-----3-3------]----|  
  E----------------------------------|]  
