  [G----------------------------------|  
  D--------------------------0-------|  
  A-----0--2-2-0--2-2-0--2-2---2-----|  
  E----------------------------------|]  
  *These are the parts, now here's the order to play them:*  
  *Intro   X6*  
  *Chorus  X1*  
  *Verse   X2*  
  *Intro   X3*  
  *Verse   X1*  
  *Intro   X3*  
  *Verse   X1*  
  *Chorus  X1*  
  **Verse  X4  (When you play the verse and chorus this time,*  
  **Chorus X1   move everything a half-step higher)*  
  *Intro   X4*  
  **Chorus X1  (Play the part in brackets 3 times)*  
  *Verse   X4*  
  **Intro  X1  (The note in brackets is the last note of the song.)*  
  
